survey_response.review_text: Very pleasant doctor, and the procedure done well with minimal pain.  There was no wait time me and the overall  experience was good.

I had a very good experience in getitng treatment done by Dr. Sandhya Karthik. She builds a rapo with teh patients which helps the patients to be confident and comfortable enough to discuss there problems clearly.

I went to doctor for the first time in May or June for getting my root canal treatment done. The treatment of root canal was painless, which is usually bit painfull. After the root canal treatment doctor prescribed me few pain killer and antibiotics.

I also had the problem of Dental floss ( skin growth between two teeth ), which was also treated by Dr. Sandhya Karthik.

Along with Dr. Sandhya Karthik, her husband also practices in the clinic who is also equally good at treatment. There wont be much delay by doctor in attending the patients.

Usually there would be a waiting of five to ten minutes. The waiting hall is tidy and doctor have two staff who are also polite as doctor, and helpfull at times.

I would be happy to recommend Dr. Sandhya Karthik to my friends and family members.

This was my first visit to Dr.Sandhya Karthik. My first impression on doctor was really very good.
I usually visit my family doctor for my dental problems. As my regular doctor was out of town on an emergency I visited Dr.Sandhya Karthik. I had sever ache in gums and teeth. Doctor listened to all my problems politely and with lot of patience. It was very comfortable for me to speak about the problem to the doctor.
Dr.Sandhya is very attentive at her treatments and she treats patients with lot of care . After basic investigations doctor suggested me to go for x-ray of my teeth, which I did not feel was irrelevant. Though this was my first consultation with the doctor i was really impressed by the way she treats her patients and the patience to listen to them. The consultation fee was also not much more compared to others.
After an emergency check up and x-ray, I followed up for treatment with my regular doctor. And now my problem of gums and teeth is solved.
Finally i would recommend this doctor to my known persons and family members as well.

1. The doctor was very patient in listening to all my problems. 
2. She gave answer to each and every query, until I was satisfied. Generally doctors do not tell us much but I must say, I was explained in details all the problems in my teeth. 
3. The whole process was transparent - I was told every thing while being treated. 

I'm highly satisfied with the treatment. Highly recommended for everyone. 
If you are new to the city, like me, just have a consultation with them, and then it up to you to get further treatment or not. 

:)

It was such a great experience with Dr. Sandhya. She is very kind, polite and generous. My overall treatment went very smoothly and I am highly satisfied with the treatment she did. The clinic ambience is very nice and hygienic. Clinic staff is also very polite and helpful. I highly recommend the doctor to everyone.

First of all there was very less waiting time and they have excellent front office staff who treat you very kindly and are also well informed about the happenings in the clinic. 
The place is neat and tidy with lovely fish tanks.
Doctors explanation about the issue is excellent, which puts the patient at ease.

*** ******* ******* ** ** ********* ******** She took the time to explain every procedure she was doing. How greatful I am that I can cite my experience with 
Dr. Sandhya ,😊 Vibha Dental Care all by itself gives such a positive vibrations, Beautiful interiors warmth and pleasant environment. I was made to feel welcome & comfortable. Dr. Sandhya by her wealth of knowledge, skill and professionalism made me feel that comfortable with her gentle touch, Kudos to Dr. Sandhya , she explained simple techniques and now that I need'nt to worry about my Dental issues.

She left a broken file(screw) inside. Which was left very deep. And even after my repeated request she didn't tried to took ut out.

And please note that she will ask for all money on first seating. 4500/- in my case. Totally wasted.

Always consult to an endodontic for rct. Never compromise with bds
